Code used in the article, "Model-Based Uncertainty"

NOTE: The MVAD data that we used for this paper is public. 

DecompVarR2.Rmd - reproduces all plots used in the paper
functions.R - simulation functions used by Simula_MC3state_comments.R
   from Bartolucci, F.; Pandolfi, S.; Pennoni, F. Parsimonious parametrizations of transition matrices 
   https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s10479-025-06986-x
Simula_MC3state_comments.R - generates simulated data used in paper (save is commented out on last line)
dat31_3.Rdata - simulated data used in the paper

Questions? Contact marc.scott@nyu.edu (corresponding author)
